    "naive": "Find patients with autoimmune disease.",
    "broad": "Find patients with any documented autoimmune condition — including rheumatologic (RA, SLE), GI (Crohn's), neurologic (MS), endocrine (T1DM), or dermatologic (psoriasis) autoimmune diseases.",
    "expert": "Search Condition for the autoimmune disease umbrella ICD-10 codes: M06.9 (RA), M32.9 (SLE), K50.9 (Crohn's), G35 (MS), E10.9 (T1DM). Query: Condition?code=http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10-cm|M06.9,http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10-cm|M32.9,http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10-cm|K50.9,http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10-cm|G35,http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10-cm|E10.9"
